title: Gaslight - Gaslight (1970/2012) [FLAC]
description:
Mega rare dark folk-psych rarity recorded 1970. Debut CD release for this UK private-pressing that was originally issued in tiny quantity. Accomplished musicianship with wandering violin, guitars and moody vocals on a mix of original, trad and classic folk tunes in similar territory to Marie Celeste, Oberon and Tickawinda.
